{"tid":596653,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(邊個痴線啲) 謝霆鋒 vs 龍心","createTime":"2018-03-17T23:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T18:22:20.000Z","uid":173542,"like":101,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3a4cc3912790564771be455a2168c3f2b9a4094b","tid":596653,"uid":173542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T23:46:01.000Z","msg":"謝霆鋒 (綽號：謝檸檬、Chief Le&rsquo;mon)<br />\n痴線事件薄<br />\n1. 盪斗直髮<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/015513_e3e44f52523d2382b81a3b51820ae0c6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F015513_e3e44f52523d2382b81a3b51820ae0c6.gif&h=bc919dc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 台上忘我<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/074531_46e18c32151bae1e279c241a33660ac6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F074531_46e18c32151bae1e279c241a33660ac6.gif&h=76fc1a67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 亂9咁啫甜品<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/015859_002b41dbac9d8888eff4cd70cca89543.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F015859_002b41dbac9d8888eff4cd70cca89543.gif&h=61b37937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 同張柏芝結婚 (俾陳冠希食過仲要有哂閃卡)<br />\nSorry Edison,阿嬌，借張相㴝頂住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/020425_9c8769ccbe74d5cba48c1994adfead04.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F020425_9c8769ccbe74d5cba48c1994adfead04.png&h=b7d4aaf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n龍心 (綽號：維園謝霆鋒)<br />\n痴線事件薄<br />\n1. 決戰牛佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/041951_f75539a40ea3bcdb0f4c8eb8e8d772d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F041951_f75539a40ea3bcdb0f4c8eb8e8d772d3.png&h=2d4654e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 維園論壇撻朵<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/042328_a4753f9271a2939da8bf14083149ab73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F042328_a4753f9271a2939da8bf14083149ab73.png&h=3b5919c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完尋日講龍心個post ，有以下嘅諗法:<br />\n龍心個樣雖然好似痴線佬，但係其實佢做嘅事係有自己背後嘅道理。<br />\n相反，謝霆鋒外表正常人，但佢啲奇異行為唔會俾龍心比下去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得<br />\n龍心，外表痴線但內裡算做正常<br />\n謝霆鋒，外表正常但內裡痴9線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 謝霆鋒 痴線啲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 龍心 痴線啲"},{"pid":"cb1a9e61db5c6504f85cc449c7af266c773bc68c","tid":596653,"uid":137166,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T23:52:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c772e93ff2b02677b24da56b6be6536a7f6df91f","tid":596653,"uid":169468,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T23:59:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實兩個都唔系太痴線...</blockquote><br />\n系你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5402b2bb5b65209a0ea45240c2d6efa649fd662","tid":596653,"uid":173542,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T00:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/080326_0846bbba292becb6fc48d1053a144a33.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg